Fstab code for adding extra harddrives for automount
I'm sure I'll be updating this a lot when I have to do reformats or get new hard drives 

# /dev/sdb1
UUID=C292A45592A44FA9       /home/ericparsley/Storage1TB       ntfs       defaults,noatime       0       2

# /dev/sdc1
UUID=F054B06854B03368       /home/ericparsley/Storage2TB       ntfs       defaults,noatime       0       2

# /dev/sdd1
UUID=2C2D1BDB2ACB6AA3       /home/ericparsley/Storage4TB       ntfs       defaults,noatime       0       2
